jsondiscoverer

Class JsonSourceSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • jsondiscoverer.AbstractJsonSource
      • jsondiscoverer.JsonSourceSet

  • public class JsonSourceSet
extends AbstractJsonSource
    This class is used to represent a set of JsonSource elements.

    In the context of JSON Discoverer, it is used to model an API, which is composed of several JSON-based Web services. As so, the JsonSourceSet includes a set of JsonSource elements and therefore each one collects the JSON documents for each JSON-based Web service.

    Author:
    Javier Canovas (me@jlcanovas.es)
